sequenceDiagram
  actor R as Recruiter
  participant API as Recruiter interviews
  participant Cal as Internal calendar + ICS
  participant DB as DB
  R->>API: Schedule interview
  API->>DB: Conflict detection
  alt conflict
    API-->>R: Warning / conflict response
  else ok
    API->>DB: Interview + participants
    API->>Cal: Internal event + ICS content
    API-->>R: Scheduled
  end
  Note over Cal: Google/Outlook Not Configured
